content: I got a variety of fruits like apples, bananas, and berries, as well as some veggies like carrots, broccoli, and cauliflower - speaking of which, I tried their new cauliflower gnocchi on Monday and it was surprisingly good! I'm open to any cuisine and meal type, but I do prefer recipes that can be ready in under 30 minutes. I also have a busy schedule, so I'd appreciate any meal prep ideas that can be reheated throughout the week.
